lead_paragraph: Assistant coach Paul Gustard has urged England to maintain their discipline in Saturday's clash against Argentina at Twickenham as World Rugby cracks down on foul play.

headline.print_headline: Rugby-England Must Maintain Discipline Against Argentina: Gustard
headline.main: Rugby-England Must Maintain Discipline Against Argentina: Gustard
